oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Corner of 11th Avenue South and Summit Avenue, 1965
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Photograph of the corner of 11th Avenue South and Summit Avenue, 1965. The area was the old site for the Edgehill Estates (Project Tenn. 5-18), and within the boundaries of the Edgehill Urban Renewal Project area (Project Tenn. R-69). Photographed by the Nashville Housing Authority. Forms part of the MDHA Photograph Collection. 1 photograph : b & w.
